        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Most residential epoxy flooring projects in Carpentersville are completed within 24-48 hours, including preparation, application, and curing time. Larger commercial projects may take 3-5 days depending on the square footage."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What areas do you serve besides Carpentersville?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "We proudly serve Carpentersville and surrounding Fox Valley communities including East Dundee, West Dundee, Sleepy Hollow, Gilberts, and Algonquin. Contact us to confirm service availability for your specific location."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you offer free estimates?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
